name: Dare (La La La)
content: 来吧 来吧 来吧 来吧
La la la I dare you
All of my life  too late
直到你在对的时候出现
And here we are you rock it
现在我们在这里，开始吧
Nothing is just like the f**king socket
I used to meet you again
Get ready we'll do it again
游戏开始了，我们再来一遍
现在不是疗伤的时候，让我们醉吧醉吧醉吧
When your eyes got me drunk I was sober
你的眼睛让我沉醉，可我如此清醒
Is it true that you love me
I dare you to kiss me
舞池的一切都这么真实
Truth or dare on the dancefloor
舞池的一切都那么真实
